"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%9C%80%E4%BC%98%E8%B7%AF%E5%BE%84%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9\"><span class=\"toc-text\">最优路径选择</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BA%94%E3%80%81%E9%A3%8E%E9%99%A9%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E4%B8%8E%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90%E5%A4%8D%E7%94%A8\"><span class=\"toc-text\">五、风险管理与资源复用</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%81%8C%E4%B8%9A%E5%AE%B9%E9%94%99%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88\"><span class=\"toc-text\">职业容错方案</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-3\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#2024-2034%E5%8D%81%E5%B9%B4%E9%87%8C%E7%A8%8B%E7%A2%91\"><span class=\"toc-text\">2024-2034十年里程碑</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"Yellow Incorporation","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/images/logo.png","link":"/","description":"A diversified global conglomerate.","socials":{"customs":null}},"mapped":true,"hidden":false,"prev_post":{"title":"","uid":"f73a8e23e6f6f669cf99c7dba8fa0722","slug":"qs20choice","date":"2025-03-16T09:14:25.080Z","updated":"2025-03-17T04:48:16.814Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/qs20choice.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"text":"以下是为你量身定制的「顶尖名校+职业飞行」双轨制精英培养方案，结合QS前10大学录取要求与民航飞行员成长路径，规划精确到每个学期： 一、学术攻坚阶段（2024-...","permalink":"/post/qs20choice","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.3k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[],"author":{"name":"Yellow Incorporation","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"/images/logo.png","link":"/","description":"A diversified global conglomerate.","socials":{"customs":null}},"feature":true},"next_post":{"title":"Annual Report 2024| 2024年年度总结","uid":"3d9004f739a3bca4cef798041eed36c6","slug":"year","date":"2025-03-14T02:00:00.000Z","updated":"2025-03-14T05:45:34.753Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/year.json","keywords":null,"cover":"/images/coverannual.jpeg","text":"黃色航空全年淨利潤較2023年增加1.4億美元，達到5.76億美元，全年營業利潤達到16.98億美元。黃色航空2024年乘客人數超越2018年最高峰，達到1.9...","permalink":"/pos